subject: Re: [junit] Failed to invoke suite():java.lang.StackOverflowError
msgSnippet: The StackOverflow is because you are calling return suite() in BeanTests.suite(). FYI: StackOverflow generally comes from a recursion you didn t mean to do
messageBody:
The StackOverflow is because you are calling "return suite()" in
BeanTests.suite().

FYI: StackOverflow generally comes from a recursion you didn't mean to do
or an infinite loop.

=jason
